text: Kurt Madsen (born 8 January 1936) is a Danish wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Denmark Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Halsnæs Municipality
